org.supercsv.prefs.CsvPreference

Packages that use CsvPreference
org.supercsv.io The IO package contains various reader/writers for reading/writing strings, maps or objects (POJO beans). 
org.supercsv.prefs This package defines the configuration classes used when instantiating readers and writers.
